(12, 326, '136805923037665_1194079503976963', 'اسوأ خدمة لما بعد البيع!\nعشان اغير قطعة غيار غسالة شركة بحجم سامسونج رافضة تجيب قطعة الغيار البيت، و لازم اروح ادفع تمنها الاول!!\nطب ماجيب الغسالة بالمرة\nايه مفهوم خدمة ما بعد البيع لسلعة كبيرة؟!\nهل ميزانية وكيل شركة بحجم سامسونج لا تحتمل تمن قطعة غيار غسالة فلازم الدفع مقدماً؟!\nاو سامسونج مصر بتوصل رسالة لعملائها احنا لا نثق فيكم بس انتوا ثقوا فينا عادى؟!', '1465212508', '2016-06-07 13:54:18', '2016-06-07 13:54:18'),
(13, 326, '136805923037665_1193985300653050', 'Complain\n\nDear Samsung group I am a loyal customer to most of all samsung products since many years especially the TV as in my opinion are the best.\nNow I faced a problem concerning my TV ( model attached) which the screen becomes white after seconds of turning on the TV. And if I manage with the brightness the screen appears as the negative of photos!!\nI contacted the agent in Egypt whom tried to help me on phone but when it did not succeed they gave a number and told me that they will call me in 2 working days . After 3 working days and no calls I in my turn called the Call Center where bizarrely a  young lady replied to say that it is an OLD model and no repair!!!! \nI am just asking :\nis a durable good would be called OLD \nIs a Samsung Model 7 years old has no any spare parts!!!???\nIn that case I would be very careful buying this brand.\nPlease Samsung Group as a loyal customer I choose first to inbox you . Waiting for a prompt reply.\n Adla Ragab PhD\nProfessor of Economics Cairo University. adla.ragab@feps.edu.eg', '1465201214', '2016-06-07 13:54:18', '2016-06-07 13:54:18'),
