(145, 326, '136805923037665_1186637011387879', 'I bought  Mobile Samsung s6 from jumbo citycentre Sharjah on 16/12/2025 including one-year warranty from date of purchase \nIn 15/4/2016.\nsuddenly the mobile turned off then i was not able to start it again or recharge the battery does not recharge, all it shows when i press turn on/off button is the signal Samsung primitive just like the next photo shows,\n\n i was in Cairo and sent mobile to Samsung Egypt, who said that the problem was in the mobile motherboard and must be sent to the place of purchase until to use the advantage of warranty\nIn 15/5/2016 i was in sharjah and went to samsung technical support i told them what happened, and the answer was better to buy a new mobile  because that the motherboard suffered damage as a result of downloading an infected program with a virus which caused the mother board damage and due to that my mobile is out of warranty coverage and they mentioned that a new motherboard costs 1350 dirhams and they added something called ( rooting ) that permited this virus download , \nWell first i only use samsung store for downloading applications and my mobile was never jail broken \nSecond i asked them how did they find out that ( rooting ) jail break was on my mobile, they replied that they turn on the device and enter some code or through about device which is impossible because the mobile does not start at all and in return i refused to receive the mobile from mentainence.\nAfterwards i contacted Samsung call center Mr. Noureddine said that the technical report did not arrive yet from jumbo and he will be in touch soon, more than 10 days and no one contacted me so yesterday i called Mr. Mohamed el kwisny he said that he did not recieve the report ..\nWhen asked if Mr. Mohammed how is it possible to know if the reason of motherboard damage was out of downloading rooting , he said the device must be turned on and either to enter some code or through about device which is impossible because the mobile does not start at all.\nFirst, i have not download any software except by using samsung store and definatly i did not download ( rooting )\nSecond, samsung egypt mentioned that the problem in motherboard is due to Manufacturing defect and mobile should be replaced in purchasing store according to warranty\nThird,samsung technical support could not access to turn on the mobile to find out what was the error, they just easily tried to deludes me that it was my mistake not theirs in order to skip warranty guarantee\n\nsamsung technical support refuses to replace the device or repair it ,\nplease help me out here either my device to be repaired or replaceed\nThank you\nSm-G920FZKAXSG\nIMEI : 359937/06/938898/1\nS/N : R58G81VTNST\n\nI was contacted  by Samsung arabia based in dubai to solve my problem regarding my mobile s6 but they assured me that my mobile did breach protection one way or another and i have asked how security could be breached, they said one way could be by downloading a program from the play store, this is one of the possibilities and I mentioned that this is the only possibility the virus was downloaded through an application in the play store cause i only use the store that is certified by samsung where I have not received any software or enter any link can contain the virus, they said that the company may not know the reason for breach security but emphasizes what happened and the added that some application may contain a virus and not all the applications on their certified store are trusted ...... Thanks to mr. Mostafa from Samsung for his attention, but if the play store is not locked and secure and anyone can upload program that contains a virus and Samsung did not inform its clients to be aware of that, how Samsung can add this store on its Mobiles and that  one of its features that it may include viruses or spams or bugs that can destroy the motherboard or the mobile\nThat did cost me the loss of my mobile that costs 2000 AED and all my data on it\nSamsung is responsible from my view, for breach of protection in my mobile by adding a non secure store without mentioning this to its users.\nRegardless it took more than 10 days and did not communicate with me about a technical report until i presented my complain online and on the sansung facebook page, \n Price of my mobile AED 2,000 and  samsung want me to fix it in less than three months at AED 1350 and they said my mobile is out of warranty because i downloaded an application through play store and the can make me a discount  of 145 dirhams \nBig Thanks to Samsung, which its goal is customer satisfactiont ...last time to deal with sumsung any where any device and i will keep spreding this everywhere to everyone', '1464217905', '2016-06-07 13:54:22', '2016-06-07 13:54:22'),
